-- Bugs Fixed and Ready For Release 
Fixed: Falling powerup objects are automatically collected by tanks
Fixed: Small ogg files not playing correctly
Fixed: MOTD is correct when it is reshown
Fixed: Music plays correctly on big endian machines (e.g. PPC macs)
Fixed: Chat tooltips have been moved out the way
Fixed: Bilboard aspect ratios in camera mode
Fixed: MIRV shot path being slightly out
Fixed: Game will switch to medium/high detail models if there are no low detail ones
Fixed: Stars not showing when specified
Fixed: Sky layers drawn correctly so flying objects can be seen behind them

Added: nohorizonglow, nosunblend and suntexturemask attributes to landscape textures to allow decent planets
Added: Console command ReloadLandscapeObjects that reloads the landscape definition from disk and re-displays
Added: Console command ShowLandscapeInfo that shows which map files are currently in use
Added: Console command ShowLandscapeAimInfo that shows the current position of the auto aim cursor ("A" key)
Added: Authentication dialog for when server needs name/password
Added: Player view on network browsing dialog
Added: Re-send functionality to chat menu
Added: Tooltips are split into two catagories (info and help) each of which can be disabled
Added: Rules tab shows options changed for this level(L) and options changed from default(*)

-- Bugs in current development release
Dvorak keyboard support is broken
Crashing when minimized during texture/level load

